frames.caption: A majestic rhinoceros stands in the middle of a sunlit desert landscape, with a large bird soaring above it. The scene is set against a backdrop of rolling sand dunes and scattered cacti.
frames.description: The image depicts a serene desert environment where a rhinoceros and a bird coexist. The bright blue sky and golden sand create a vivid contrast, highlighting the natural beauty of the scene.

frames.caption: A fantastical creature, resembling a rhinoceros with large wings, charges forward across a sandy desert landscape. The creature's wings are spread wide, creating a dramatic and surreal scene against the clear blue sky.
frames.description: The scene depicts a mythical creature in a desert setting, combining elements of a rhinoceros and a bird. The creature is in motion, kicking up sand as it moves, creating a sense of power and fantasy.
